<HEAD>WASHINGTON TODAY: Deficit Panel Still Shaky, Despite Bush Action</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By MARTIN CRUTSINGER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
