<HEAD>Red Cross Says Armenia Needs Money, Limbs, But No More Shipments</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Soviet-Quake, Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By TONY CZUCZKA</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>GENEVA (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
