 <PERSON> Ruth </PERSON> <PERSON> Sinai </PERSON> covered the <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> East </LOCATION> for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> for four years and now reports on foreign policy for the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>.
