tely to begin whatever work is necessary to improve the safety conditions at these plants.'' <PERSON> Fitzwater </PERSON> also said, `` I repeat the president's statement that no plant will be operated until it's safe, and that's why we thought it was crucial to get this money on the project early, and the supplemental is not a good way to go.''
